# Hostinger / production build: DATABASE_URL must be available when `npm run build` runs so
# migrations apply and the catalog seeds on an empty database. Redeploys skip catalog re-seed
# (and do not delete orders) unless you set FORCE_SEED=1.
# FORCE_SEED=1
# SKIP_SEED=1
